comments: Powell (DAL) sets the screen on Barnes (SAC) and does not deliver contact.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Brunson (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Barnes (SAC).
Powell (DAL) makes contact with Barnes' (SAC) arm and affects his driving shot attempt, causing the ball to go out of bounds.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) sets the screen on Brunson (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LLB and RLS show Brunson (DAL) makes clean contact with the ball as he dislodges it from Fox (SAC) during the shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) sets the screen on Barnes (SAC) and does not deliver contact.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Doncic (DAL).
Barnes (SAC) and Powell (DAL) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Bogdanovic (SAC) and Brunson (DAL) make incidental contact with each other as they move to the same spot on the floor.
Broekhoff (DAL) moves his foot heel-to-toe to create space.
Bogdanovic (SAC) and Kleber (DAL) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Hield (SAC) wraps Powell (DAL) and dislodges him from his position.
Kleber (DAL) makes marginal contact with Bogdanovic (SAC) and does not affect his ability to pass.
Doncic (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Fox (SAC).
Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact to Fox (SAC) as he moves alongside his body during his driving shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Doncic (DAL) lifts his pivot foot before releasing his dribble.
Barnes (SAC) has his forearm rested on Doncic's (DAL) body during his driving shot attempt and does not extend it into him to deliver contact.
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Powell (DAL) and Barnes (SAC) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Fox (SAC) grabs Powell (DAL) after he gathers the rebound and affects his SQBR.
Broekhoff (DAL) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Barnes (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Doncic (DAL).
